data.description: Welcome to this exquisite brick home located in the highly sought-after neighborhood. This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home is waiting for you. Boasting a spacious layout with two distinct living areas, this residence offers ample room for both relaxation and entertainment.  Enjoy the luxury of two spacious living areas, providing versatility for your lifestyle needs. Elegant hardwood floors grace the interiors, adding warmth and character to every room. This home offers a dedicated office space that also has an underground storm shelter. The kitchen offers ample counter space, modern appliances, and a layout designed for efficiency. A dedicated laundry room adds to the practicality and organization of this home, along with a large pantry and plenty of storage cabinets. The attached garage provides secure parking for two vehicles and additional storage space. Centrally located, this home is surrounded by amenities and offers easy access to Altus Air Force Base, Quartz Mountain State Park, and many restaurants and local shopping.
